  {"id": "doctor-suspect-git-human",
   "sandbox": {"setup": [
     {"step": "git", "commits": [
       {"date": "2024-03-05T10:00:00+02:00", "message": "pin: base corpus",
        "write": [
          {"path": "corpus/adr-001.md",
           "content": "# ADR-001: Referring Choice\n\n## Context\n\nDoctor needs a referrer whose target changed later.\n\n## Decision\n\nReference the sibling decision.\n\n## Consequences\n\nThe drift phase flags this artifact as suspect.\n\n## Status\n\nAccepted\n\n## Related Decisions\n\n- adr-002\n"},
          {"path": "corpus/adr-002.md",
           "content": "# ADR-002: Moving Target Choice\n\n## Context\n\nDoctor needs a target committed after its referrer.\n\n## Decision\n\nChange in a later commit.\n\n## Consequences\n\nThe referrer becomes suspect.\n\n## Status\n\nAccepted\n"}
        ]},
       {"date": "2024-04-01T09:30:00-05:00", "message": "pin: revise target",
        "write": [
          {"path": "corpus/adr-002.md",
           "content": "# ADR-002: Moving Target Choice\n\n## Context\n\nDoctor needs a target committed after its referrer.\n\n## Decision\n\nChange in a later commit.\n\n## Consequences\n\nThe referrer becomes suspect.\n\n## Status\n\nAccepted\n\nRevised in a later commit.\n"}
        ]}
     ]}
   ]},
   "cwd": "{SANDBOX}",
   "argv": ["doctor", "corpus"],
   "expect_exit": 0},
